<h2 id="_inserting_template_variables">4. Inserting template variables</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The data provided by Janolaw will be integrated using <strong>template variables</strong>.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_online_store">4.1. Online store</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Insert the template variables into the corresponding <strong>categories</strong> or <strong>templates</strong> of your online store.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the following <strong>template variables</strong> to integrate the data into your <strong>online store</strong>:</p>
</div>
