<h2 id="_menu_legal_information">5. Menu: Legal information</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you are using the service provided by Janolaw, then you can find the data or texts that they offer by going to <strong><a href="/omni-channel/online-store/setting-up-clients/online-store#legal-information">Settings » Client (store) » Standard » Online store » Legal information  </a></strong>. In this menu, check to make sure that all data was transmitted and displayed correctly.</p>
</div>
